\u8216?Yes,\u8217? said he to himself, \u8216?for long enough my bed was dry and prickly, and now it is as soft as roses. But what will the serpent turn out to be?\u8217?\par\pard\plain\hyphpar}{\par\pard\hyphpar }{\page } {\s1 \afs32
